- All documentation pages must use Nextra 4.0 syntax (app/ directory and Next.js App Router).
- Do not use theme.config.js or the legacy pages/ directory.
- Document structure must be app/docs/xxx/page.mdx, with navigation and metadata set in layout.tsx.
- The theme should be nextra-theme-docs, with sidebar and TOC via layout.tsx.
- If internationalization is needed, use Next.js App Router i18n in layout.tsx.